    <body>
      <section eId="sec_1266_J">
        <num>1266-J</num>
        <heading>Metropolitan transportation authority pledge to customers</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1266_J__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>a description of the authority's commitment to provide safe and\nreliable services;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1266_J__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>a description of the authority's commitment to provide timely and\naccurate information on its services;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1266_J__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>a commitment that employees will provide service in a courteous\nmanner;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1266_J__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>a description of the authority's commitment to maintain clean\nstations, facilities, subways and buses;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1266_J__subsec_e">
          <num>(e)</num>
          <content>
            <p>a description of the authority's policies when it comes to\narranging alternative transportation when service is interrupted;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1266_J__subsec_f">
          <num>(f)</num>
          <content>
            <p>when service is interrupted, a description of the authority's\npolicies when it comes to considering the comfort of inconvenienced\ncustomers;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1266_J__subsec_g">
          <num>(g)</num>
          <content>
            <p>when service is interrupted due to weather conditions, a\ndescription of the authority's policies on notifying customers;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1266_J__subsec_h">
          <num>(h)</num>
          <content>
            <p>when service is severely interrupted, a description of the\nauthority's policies on service restoration.\n  3. The authority from time to time may, update and amend the\nmetropolitan transportation authority pledge to customers as it deems\nnecessary and proper and may adopt rules and regulations for the proper\nadministration of this section.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
